endered":"<p>目前我用的是 Self-hosted LiveSync 同步方案， 使用自己搭建的 CouchDB 服务器，如果仅仅同步文档数据没什么问题。</p>\n<p>但是我想同步插件和设置，不想在每个设备上重复的配置，也就是同步 .obsidian 目录。</p>\n<p>开启 .obsidian 同步之后体验就不是很好了，每次在其它设备上打开 Obsidian 总是要等待同步很大半天，而且同步期间还经常需要多次重启应用，重新加载配置，而且还时不时会出现冲突文件需要手动解决，体验很不丝滑。</p>\n<p>目前使用 Obsidian 需要在三台设备之间同步：Mac 、IOS 、Windows 。</p>\n<p>请教一下大家平时使用 Obsidian ，用的跨设备同步方案是什么？有没有体验与 Saas 软件类似的比较丝滑的同步方案？</p>\n","last_modified":1700622504,"replies":74,"id":994099},{"node":{"avatar_large":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/e96e/d478/218_large.png?m=1650127724","name":"podcast","avatar_normal":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/e96e/d478/218_normal.png?m=1650127724","title":"Podcast","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/go/podcast","topics":152,"footer":"","header":"","title_alternative":"Podcast","avatar_mini":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/e96e/d478/218_mini.png?m=1650127724","stars":318,"aliases":[],"root":false,"id":218,"parent_node_name":"geek"},"member":{"id":648418,"username":"boomer995","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/u/boomer995","website":null,"twitter":null,"psn":null,"github":null,"btc":null,"location":null,"tagline":null,"bio":null,"avatar_mini":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/8866aa400461037c1405e899473ec63f?s=24&d=retro","avatar_normal":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/8866aa400461037c1405e899473ec63f?s=48&d=retro","avatar_large":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/8866aa400461037c1405e899473ec63f?s=73&d=retro","created":1694593197,"last_modified":1697855313},"last_reply_by":"tracyliu","last_touched":1700642720,"title":"大家都在听什么播客?","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/t/994034","created":1700616318,"deleted":0,"content":"想看看大家平时都在听些什么样的播客呢?愿意的话,就分享下你最近最喜欢的 1-2 个播客,最好能简单介绍一下它的主题和独特之处。","content_rendered":"想看看大家平时都在听些什么样的播客呢?愿意的话,就分享下你最近最喜欢的 1-2 个播客,最好能简单介绍一下它的主题和独特之处。","last_modified":1700624954,"replies":64,"id":994034},{"node":{"avatar_large":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/c74d/97b0/16_large.png?m=1650127281","name":"share","avatar_normal":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/c74d/97b0/16_normal.png?m=1650127281","title":"分享发现"